                      <p>â€¢ Temperature sensors</p>
                      <p>â€¢ Motion sensors</p>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 italic">Other acceptable answers: Light sensors, Pressure sensors, Distance sensors, Touch sensors</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </details>
            </div>
            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="mb-8 p-6 bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
